---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="LatteArtist Support"
    description="Get support for the LatteArtist app - your personal latte art progress tracker"
    ogTitle="LatteArtist Support"
    ogDescription="Get support for the LatteArtist app - your personal latte art progress tracker"
    ogUrl="https://latteartist.coffeeatpetros.com/support"
    twitterTitle="LatteArtist Support"
    twitterDescription="Get support for the LatteArtist app - your personal latte art progress tracker"
>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 mb-4">
        <h1
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold mb-4 text-title-light dark:text-title-dark"
        >
            LatteArtist Support
        </h1>

        <div
            class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none prose-p:text-foreground prose-headings:text-title-light dark:prose-headings:text-title-dark prose-a:text-link hover:prose-a:text-link-hover prose-strong:text-foreground"
        >
            <h2>About LatteArtist</h2>
            <p>
                LatteArtist is a personal latte art progress tracking app designed to help coffee enthusiasts document and improve their latte art skills. The app allows you to track your pours, save your favorite designs, and monitor your progress over time.
            </p>

            <h2>Getting Support</h2>
            <p>
                If you need help with the LatteArtist app, have questions about features, or want to report an issue, please contact us at:
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:petros@coffeeatpetros.com">petros@coffeeatpetros.com</a>
            </p>
            <p>
                We typically respond to support requests within 24-48 hours. Please include details about:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>The device you're using (iPhone model, iOS version)</li>
                <li>The app version you're running</li>
                <li>A description of the issue or question</li>
                <li>Steps to reproduce the problem (if applicable)</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Common Questions</h2>
            <p>
                For general questions about app functionality, feature requests, or feedback, please don't hesitate to reach out. We're always looking to improve the app based on user feedback.
            </p>

            <h2>Privacy & Data</h2>
            <p>
                LatteArtist prioritizes your privacy. The app does not collect personally identifying information and only uses anonymous usage data to improve the app experience. For complete details about our privacy practices, please review our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>.
            </p>

        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>